==Stage 1==
===Trying to identify or capture before picking a side===
* {{mes|Talk to either the Guard or Goblin recruiter to take part in this event.}}

===Guard side===
* '''Guard Recruiter:''' Another recruit looking to enlist in D.U.N.G?
* '''Player:''' D.U.N.G?
* '''Guard Recruiter:''' Yes, the Defences United against Nasty Goblins.
* '''Player:''' How come I've never heard of them before?
* '''Guard Recruiter:''' Okay, I made it up. It's my first day and I wanted to promote a united attitude.
* '''Guard Recruiter:''' We suspect there's a Goblin uprising on the horizon and the Goblins are sending spies to seek out weak spots in the city.
* '''Guard Recruiter:''' Will you join us in locating and defending Falador?
* {{tselect|Do you want to enlist with the Guards?}}
* {{topt|Yes}}
** '''Player:''' I'm in.
** '''Guard Recruiter:''' Good. Your mission, should you one day have a choice of accepting it, is to locate and capture any Goblins you suspect of being spies.
** '''Guard Recruiter:''' We want to interrogate them and find out what they're up to!
** {{tselect|An interface will be open during the period of this event when ever you're in the event area. Do you want to toggle this off?}}
** {{topt|Yes}}
** {{topt|No}}
* {{topt|No}}
** '''Player:''' Not for now, thanks.
** '''Guard Recruiter:''' Fine, but don't let the destruction of Falador sit on your conscience.
** {{tact|end}}

====If aligned with the guards====
* '''Guard Recruiter:''' No time to lose, recruit, identify those Goblin spies as fast as you can!
* {{tact|end}}

====If aligned with the goblins====
* '''Guard Recruiter:''' How could you! I hope you're serving as an informant on the inside of the Goblin front you traitor!
* {{tact|end}}

===Goblin side===
* '''Goblin Recruiter:''' Puny human, you want to enlist in Goblin invasion?
* '''Player:''' Goblin Invasion?
* '''Goblin Recruiter:''' Yes. After defeat last year, we're rising up again to defeat smaller more stupid town this time.
* '''Goblin Recruiter:''' Our intelligence suggests town has spies who try to see what we Goblins are up to.
* '''Player:''' Goblins and intelligence; two words I'd never of put in the same sentence.
* '''Goblin Recruiter:''' Shut up human, we have spies too ya'know. You joining us or what?
* {{tselect|Do you want to enlist with the Goblins?}}
* {{topt|Yes}}
** '''Player:''' Yeah, I fancy myself on the rebellious side.
** '''Goblin Recruiter:''' Good. Now go to stupid small town of Falador and find there{{sic}} stupid spies. They threaten our mission of takin' over.
** {{tselect|An interface will be open during the period of this event when ever you're in the event area. Do you want to toggle this off?}}
** {{topt|Yes}}
** {{topt|No}}
* {{topt|No}}
** '''Player:''' No thanks, I'm not one for anarchy.
** '''Goblin Recruiter:''' Fine, stupid human, as long as you not join stupid Falador.
** {{tact|end}}

====If aligned with the guards====
* '''Goblin Recruiter:''' You chose wrong side, puny human!
* {{tact|end}}

====If aligned with the goblins====
* '''Goblin Recruiter:''' Get to work then! Identify guard scum!
* {{tact|end}}

